+--------+
|Synopsis|
+--------+

The Hunt is made up of more than just the final moments. Preparation, location, game type, weapon choice, and ammunition all factor into what happens in those last, frantic minutes. Bass Pro Shops: The Hunt - Trophy Showdown lets you stalk your prey in eight different regions through three seasons. Prove you are a master huntsman in The Hunt Champions Tournament and win real prizes. Hit Bass Pro Shops for the latest gear, guns, and ammo, to check your trophy collection, and more. You can hunt with your normal controls or with The Bullseye Pro gun.

+-------------+
|What Is This?|
+-------------+

This torrent contains a Nintendo Wii Game in WBFS format, which is actually just a compressed ISO image. It is important to note that your Wii reads this file directly from a hard drive (there is really no need to convert it). However, this game can easily be converted back to a full-size ISO faster than it takes to extract a ZIP file using either of these programs for Windows or Mac:
